Objective
It provides a common platform to connect student and teacher online.The registered taecher can create a quiz and student can take quiz and can asses himself/herself.

Users of the System
1. Teacher
2. Student

Functionality
1. Teacher will create a quiz.
2. Teacher will add options for each questions that are to be put in the quiz.
3. Teacher shall put the correct option for respective questions, which will be displayed after the  test ends.
4. Teacher can add time limit.
5. Student can search for the quiz based on the topic.
6. Student can view which questions they have marked/not marked.
7. After test ends, Students can view the correct ans for each questions.
8. Leaderboard based on the correct responses marked by the students.

